Mwathani ekuuga atiri: mundu aakoruo ni anyenda, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arimenyagirira uuge wakwa; nake awa ni arimwendaga, na ni turiuka kuri we, </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI,      </s></f><i><fArial Black><s1846>JOHANA 15:9-17</s></f></i>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA MARUA MUTHURE JOHANA.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io Yesu akiira arumiriri ake: O ta uria ithe witu anyendete, noguo ndimwendete inyui; </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ikaragai ona wendo wakwa. Mwatura mumenyereire maathani makwa, muguikara o na wendo wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o ta uria nii nduire menyagirira maathani ma Awa, ngaikara ona wendo wake. ndamuira maundu macio, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>niigetha mugie na gikeno kiria ndi nakio, nakio gikeni kianyu gikinyanire. </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Riri nirio riathani riakwa, ati muendane inyui ene, o ta uria nii ndimwendete. </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Gutiri mundu wi na wendani munene gukira uyu ati mundu arute muoyo wake ni undu wa arata ake. </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui muri arata akwa, mweka maundu maria ndimuathaga. Ndigucoka kumwita ndungata, </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondu ndungata ndimenyaga uria mumiathi egwika; inyuiri, ndimutuite arata, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ni gukoruo inyui nindimumenyithitie maundu mothe maria njiguite hari Awa. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ti inyui mwathurire nii, ni nii ndamuthurire inyui, ngimwamura, nigetha muthii muciare maciaro, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>namo maciaro manyu matuure; niguo undu o wothe mukahoya Ithe witu na ritwa riakwa, akamuhe. </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiramwatha uguo, ni getha mwendanage.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injiri theru ya Mwathani</s></f>"}],
