Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na thiri wayo wa ciringi igana rimwe :nayo ikimukumbata, ikiminyita mümero, ikimwira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndiha thiri wakwa. Ni ündü wa üguo ngombo io yarutaga wira nayo ikiigüithia thi ikimuthaitha, : </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tiga guthethükira na ni ngaküriha. Nayo ikirega , igithii, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
