Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRI ANDŨ A KOLOSAI:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, hakĩrĩ ũguo-rĩ, mũngĩkorũo nĩ mwariũkire </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hamwe na Kristũ no kĩmathagei maũndũ marĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
