Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akristũ makumie– Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kristũ Atarĩ na wĩhia– Nĩ aigwithanirie Ithe na ehia</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ikua na ũtũũro igĩcemanio ikĩrũa</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũnene wa ũtũũro arĩ mũkuũ agĩathana arĩ muoyo</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akristũ makumie– Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Twĩre Marĩa wonire kĩ njĩra-inĩ? Nĩ ndonire mbĩrĩra </s></f>"},{ID:14,
