Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Araika marĩ aira, matama ma nguo Kristũ mwĩhoko wakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ariũkĩte. Nĩakamatongoria Galilea</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akristũ makumie– Ithĩnja rĩa Paska Gatũrũme nĩ kahonokirie ng’ondu</s></f>"},{ID:15,
