Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO KATIKA KITABU CHA NABII YONA</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana lilimjia Nabii Yona;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>''Simama, uende Ninawi, ule mji mkubwa,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ukautangazie niliyokuamuru''</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yona akasimama akenda Ninawi kwa amri ya Bwana</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi Ninawi ulikuwa mji mkubwa mbele ya Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ukubwa wake ulikuwa mwendo wa siku tatu.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alipokwisha ingia mjini wa siku moja</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yona alianza kuhubiri, akisema</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>''Baada ya siku arobaini utaangamizwa''</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Watu wa Ninawi wakamsadiki Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakautangaza ufungo kwa wakubwa </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na wadogo na wakavaa magunia.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu alipoona waliyoyafanyaa</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>jinsi walivyo acha mwenendo wao </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mbaya aliwaonea huruma na akaacha </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuwaletea uharibifu
aliotangaza kwamba atauleta</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana (TUMSHURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
Zaburi 25:4bc—5ab, 6-7bc, 8-9</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako; unijulishe mapito yako.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uniongoze katika uaminifu wako, unifundishe, </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana wewe ndiwe Mungu Mwokozi wangu. </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Bwana, ukumbuke huruma yako; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na rehema zako, maana ni za tangu milele.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Unikumbuke kwa kadiri ya upendo wako. </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Bwana ni mwema, tena mwenye haki, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa hiyo huwajulisha wakosefu njia zake.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huwaongoza wanyenyekevu katika haki, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kuwafundisha njia yake. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIITIKIO; Ee Bwana, unionyeshe njia zako.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI	I Wakorintho 7:29-31 </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu, nasema hivi: muda ni mfupi.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi, walio na wake, wawe kama hawana.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wenye kulia machozi, wawe kama hawalii.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wenye kufurahi, wawe kama hawafurahi. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na wenye kununua, wawe kama hawana kitu. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wenye kutumia ulimwengu huu, wawe kama hawautumii.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa maana mambo ya ulimwengu huu yanapita.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno Ia Bwana. 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI	
Marko 1:15</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.Aleluya.
Ufalme wa Mungu umekaribia. </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tubuni na kuiamini Injili. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI	</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo Ia Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko 
(UTUKUFU KWAKO EE BWANA)</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Baada ya Yohane kufungwa gerezani, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu alifika Galilaya akaihubiri Injili ya ufalme wa Mungu, akisema,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Wakati umefika, na ufalme wa Mungu umekaribia.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tubuni na kuiamini Injili.\"</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akitembea kando ya Bahari ya Galilaya, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>alimwona Simoni na Andrea ndugu yake </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakitupa wavu baharini, maana walikuwa wavuvi.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akawaambia,
\"Njoni mnifuate, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nami nitawafanya kuwa wavuvi wa watu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Basi wakaziacha nyavu zao na mara wakamfuata. </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akaendelea mbele kidogo, akamwona Yakobo, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwana wa Zebedayo na Yohane ndugu yake.</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Walikuwa chomboni wakizitengeneza nyavu zao.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mara akawaita.
Wakamwacha baba yao, Zebedayo, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
