"},{Guid:"Yt4+yVzdWEKrNg0TbOtYYA",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA EPIPHANIA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KUTOKEA KWAKE BWANA YESU (EPIFANIA)</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA	
Isaya 60: I-6</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Nabii Isaya</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amka! Uangaze, ewe Yerusalemu, kwa kuwa nuru yako imekuja, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao utukufu wa Bwana umekaa juu yako. Tazama, giza limeifunika dunia, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na giza kuu limeyafunika mataifa, lakini juu yako Bwana atatokea, </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao utukufu wake utaonekana juu yako. Mataifa watatembea katika </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwanga wako, nao wafalme katika weupe wa alfajiri yako.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Inua macho, utazame pande zote; wote wamekusanyika, wanakujia </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wana wako watakuja toka mbali, binti zako wanabebwa kiunoni.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa kuona hayo, utatiwa nuru, moyo wako utapendezwa nayo na kuona raha; </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maana mali ya nchi za ng'ambo ya bahari zitakujia, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na utajiri wa mataifa utakujia kwa wingi.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Makundi ya ngamia watakufunika, ngamia vijana wa Midiani na Efa.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Watu wa Sheba watakuja, wakileta dhahabu na ubani, na kutangaza sifa za Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA 
Zaburi 72: 7-8, 10-11. 12-13</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ee Mungu, umpe mfalme hukumu yako; na mwana wa mfalme haki yako; </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ahukumu taifa lako kwa haki, na wanyonge kwa usawa. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika siku zake haki iendelee, na amani izidi mpaka mwezi ukome.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atawale toka bahari hata bahari, na toka ule mto hata miisho ya dunia. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wafalme wa Tarshishi na visiwa watatoa kodi, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wafalme wa Sheba na Seba wataleta zawadi.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wafalme wote wa dunia watamwangukia, mataifa yote watamtumikia. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Maana atamkomboa maskini mwenye kumlilia, </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mnyonge asiye na msaidizi. Atamhurumia na mhitaji, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na anayaokoa maisha ya wahitaji. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio: Mataifa yote ya ulimwengu watakusujudia, ee Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
Waefeso 3:2-3a,5,6</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu:Nadhani mmesikia jinsi Mungu alivyonikabidhi neema </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya kuwasaidia ninyi, yaani kwa kunifunulia ujuzi wa fumbo, kwa wazee wa zamani</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>fumbo hilo halikujulikana kama lilivyofunuliwa sasa na Roho kwa mitume</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na manabii wake watakatifu.
Maana sasa watu wa Mataifa hurithi pamoja </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nasi pia mviungo vya mwili mmoja nasi, na wanashiriki </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ahadi moja nasi katika Kristu Yesu kwa njia ya Injili.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI 
Mathayo 2; 2</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya. Aleluya. Tuliona nyota yake mashariki. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tumekuja kumwabudu Bwana. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI
Mathayo 2:1-12</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Mathayo</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu alipozaliwa Bethlehemu wa Yudea wakati wa mfalme Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tazama, mamajusi wa mashariki walifika Yerusalemu, wakisema, </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Yuko wapi aliyezaliwa 
mfalme wa Wayahudi? </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa maana tuliona nyota yake mashariki. Tumekuja kumwabudu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mfalme Herode aliposikia hayo, alihangaika sana, na Yerusalemu yote pamoja naye. </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akawakusanya makuhani wakuna Waandishi wote wa watu, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawauliza mahali pa kuzaliwa Kristu. Nao wakamwambia, \"Bethlehemu ya Yudea, </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa maana nabii ameandikwa hivi: 'Ee Bethlehemu, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika nchi ya Yuda, huwi kamwe mji wa mwisho </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kati ya miji mikubwa ya Yuda, kwa maana kwako </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atatokea kiongozi 
atakayewachunga watu wangu Israeli. \"</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hapo Herode akawaita 
mamajusi kwa faragha, </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akawahoji kuhusu wakati 
nyota ile ilipotokea. </s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Akawatuma waende Bethlehemu akisema, </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Nendeni mkapeleleze kwa bidii habari za mtoto. </s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mkimkuta, nipasheni habari, ili nami pia niende nikamwabudu.\" </s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Walimsikiliza mfalme, wakaenda. Na tazama, nyota </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ile waliyoiona katika nchi ya mashariki ikawatangulia tena, </s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hata ilipofika ikasimama juu ya mahali alipokuwapo mtoto. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Walipoiona tena nyota, 
walifurahi kwa furaha kubwa sana. </s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakaingia nyumbani, 
wakamwona mtoto pamoja na Maria mama yake. </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakaanguka, wakamwabudu. 
Wakafungua hazina zao, </s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakamtolea zawadi za dhahabu, ubani na manemane. </s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wakiisha kuonywa katika 
ndoto wasimrudie Herode, </s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wakarudi nchini kwao kwa njia nyingine.</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
