Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>KIUMIA KIA MIRONGO IRI NA INYA MWAKA A</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA MBERE	
Sirach 27: 30 - 28: 7</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SIRACH</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Urakari na wirihiria,ni maündü moru, namo meeri makoragwo na mündü mwihia. </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Uria wothe wendaga kwirihiria, ni arimenyaga wirihiria wa Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>üria üririkanaga mawihia ma mündü.
Kiririria mündü üria üngi ihitia riria </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agwikite, na riria ükühoya, ni üriohagirüo mehia maku. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mündi angikorüo ni aigaga marakara na mündü üria üngi-ri, akihota gweterera ükiririria kuuma küri </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani? I angikiaga küigwira mündü take tha-ri, akihota gükiriririo mehia make wee </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiri mündi üria üigaga marakara ngoro-ini yake - ri: nüü üngikimükiririria mawihia make ?</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ririkana maündü ma ürigia na tiga güthürana, ririkana übuthu na ikua na urümagie mawathi. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ririkana mawathi na ndügaikare üri na muku na mündü o ürikü;</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makiria ririkana kirikaniro kia uria Uri-lgürü ma, na üriganirüo ni mahitia maria wikitwo.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GÜCOKERÜO
Thaburi 103: 1-2; 3-4; 9-10; 11.12 </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>l. Ngoro yakwa, gatha Mwathani; gwata kiria o giothe thiini wakwa nikigathe ritwa riake riamüre.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoro yakwa, kigathe Mwathani, na ndukariganiruo ni wega o na ümwe maria agwikaga</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>2.Ari we ükuohagira waganu waku wothe, ndüari ciaku ciothe o nacio nowe mukuhonia;</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we muküüri muoyo waku hari irima ria gikuü, na nowe mügwiki maündü </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ma ütugi na ma matha maigü, ta ari thumbi aragwikira ya unene.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>3.Ndangiikara o acirithanagia hindi ciothe, na ndangitüüra arakarite nginya tene na tene. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndatwikite ta üria mahitia maitü maagiriirüo, kana agatücokeria küringana na üria waganu witü üigana .</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>4.Ni amu, oguo matu-ini kühacite o igürü ria thi, no taguo ütugi wake üneneheire aria amwitigiri.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O ta aria irathiro küraihaniriirie na ithüiro, no taguo atüthengeirie mehia maitu matüraihiririe .</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Mwathani ni wa matha maingi na ni muuma andü müno.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA IGIRl	
Aroma 14 : 7- 9</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÚTHOMA MARÜA MA MÜTHURE PAUL KURI ANDU A ROMA</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aruna aitü, ithui-ri , gütiri mündu o na umwe utuuraga no ündü wake wiki,</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na gükua gütiri ükuaga no ündü wake wiki. </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ündü tungikoruo tugutuura muoyo, twatüüra türi a Mwathani ;</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tüngikorüo tükuite, twakua türi o ro a Mwathani tondu ucio-ri o na küngituika ni riu türi muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na kana riria tüngikorüo tükuite - ri , türi o a mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Amu ühoro üyü níguo watümire Kristü akue na acoke muoyo, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ati niguo atuike Mwathani o wa aria maanakua na wa aria mari muoyo .</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kiugo cia Mwathani .</s></f>"},{ID:39,
