Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI	
Mathayo 18 : 21 -35</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJIRI THERU TA URIA YANDIKITWO NI MUTHURE MATHAYO</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindi io Petro agiüka kuri Yesu akimuuria atiri : </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani, muru wa Awa anginjihia manjihia maigana ngimuohagira? </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni maita mugwanja? Yesu akimwira atirii: Ndigükwira ati, no kinya maita mügwanja; </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no riri, kaba mirongo mugwanja maita mugwanja.Ni ündu ücio üthamaki wa lgürü </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni wa kühaananio na müthamaki muna uria wendaga kuheo uhoro wa mbia ciake ni ngombo ciake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na aambiriria kwiruo ühoro ucio, ngombo imwe yari na thiri wake wa taranda ngiri ikümi .</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na tondü ni yaremetwo ni küriha, mwathani wayo agiathana ati yendio, yo nyene na mütumia wayo,</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ciana, o na indo ciayo ciothe, ni getha thiri ürihike. Ni ündü ücio ngombo io ikiigüithia thi ikimüthaitha,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikimwiraga atiri: Mwathani, tiga güthethükira na ni ngaküriha wothe. Na mwathani wa ngombo io </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiringwo ni tha, akimiohera, akimirekera thiri ücio.
No riri, ngombo io ikiumagara </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikiona ngombo ingi yarutaga wira nayo, na yari </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na thiri wayo wa ciringi igana rimwe :nayo ikimukumbata, ikiminyita mümero, ikimwira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndiha thiri wakwa. Ni ündü wa üguo ngombo io yarutaga wira nayo ikiigüithia thi ikimuthaitha, : </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tiga guthethükira na ni ngaküriha. Nayo ikirega , igithii, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikimiikithia korokoro-ini, o nginya riria ikariha thiri ücio.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riria ngombo iria ingi ciarutaga wira nayo cionire üria gwekirüo,igikiigua kieha müno, ikiira </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwathani wacio ühoro ücio wothe.
Hindi io mwathani wayo akimita akimira atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wee ngombo ino njaganu, ngürekeire thiri ücio wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni ündü ni üthaithire:
githi ndükwagiriirüo o nawe ni </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>küiguira tha ngombo iria mürutaga wira nayo,o ta üguo nii na nii ngüiguiriire tha? </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake mwathani wayo akirakara, akimineana kwi aherithania </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikohwo o nginya riria ikariha thiri ucio wothe. Uguo </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>noguo Awa uria wi iguru akamwika inyui , </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mungiaga kuohanagira na ma o mundu na muru wa ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>injiri ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
