Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia: Menyithia njira ciaku, Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ririkana matha maku, o nayo mituganire yaku, Mwathani; </s></f>"},{ID:29,
