Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>(UKUMIO KURI WEE MWATHANI)</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thutha wa Johana arikia kunyitwo, Yesu agikinya bururi wa Galilea </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiumburaga Injiri, ya Ngai akiugaga atiri; Hingo ni ihingite, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo uthamaki wa Ngai ni ukuhiririirie; wirirei, na mwitikie Injiri. </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na riria athiaga na rutere rwa iria ria Galilea ni onire Simone na Andrea, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
