Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũkani, tũkũngũiye Mwathani tũkenete, tũkĩanĩrĩre ndũmba iitũ ya ihiga, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yo nyene ũhonokia witũ. Nĩ tũkinye ũthiũ-inĩ wake twĩ na ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũmwanĩrĩre na gĩkeno tũkĩinaga nyĩmbo cia thaburi.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia: Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gĩũkeni, tũmũthathaiye, 
tũmĩinamĩrĩre; nĩ tũturĩrie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwathani ndu, o ũcio Mũtũũmbi. 
Nĩ gũkorũo we nĩwe Ngai witũ, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩ ithuĩ kĩrĩndĩ gĩake 
kwĩrĩithĩria , </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ithuĩ ng’ondu iria atungataga na gwoko gwake.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia:	Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tigai kũũmia ngoro cianyu, ta ũrĩa mwekire kũu Meriba, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthĩ to ũrĩa mwarĩ Massa, kũu werũ-inĩ; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hĩndĩ ĩrĩa maithe manyu maangeririe, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>makĩndoria, na magĩkĩona wĩko wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icokia:	Mwathani, ũtũteithie tũthikĩrĩrie mũgambo waku</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ			
1 Akorintho 7:32-35</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ AKORINTHO</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, inyuĩ-rĩ, ndenda mũikare </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũtegũtangĩka nĩ mĩhang’o. Mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtahikanĩtie ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia Mwathani; no ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhikanĩtie ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia mũtumia wake. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ningĩ ũhoro wa mũtumia wĩ na mũrũme wake nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũtiganĩte na wa mũirĩtu.  
Ũcio ũtarĩ aahika </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma Mwathani, ahotage </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gũikara emwamũre mwĩrĩ o na muoyo; no ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũhikĩte ahang’agĩra maũndũ ma thĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amenyage ũrĩa angĩkenia mũthuri we. </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo ũhoro ũcio ndawaria nĩ getha mũgunĩke inyuĩ ene,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ti ndĩmwĩkĩre mũhĩndo ngingo, no nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndĩmuonie maũndũ marĩa maagĩrĩire, na nĩ getha </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũikarage mwĩheanĩte kwĩ Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũtekũgucĩrĩrio nĩ maũndũ mangĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RUIMBO RWA ALLELUYA	Luka 7:16</s></f>"},{ID:14,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Allelluya Alleluya. Kaî gwitu nî guukîrîte munabii mănene-Î: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai nî acereire andu ake Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Marko 1:21-28</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE MARKO:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Yesu aikarĩte Kafarnao, nake o </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũthenya wa thabatũ wakinya agĩtonya </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thinagoga akĩgwata kũruta andũ ũhoro. </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao makĩgega nĩ ũhoro ũrĩa aarutanaga: tondũ </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aamarutaga ta mũndũ wathanaga, na tĩ ta </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aandĩki-marũa.  Na ihinda, o rĩu kũu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thinagoga yao gũgĩkorũo kwĩ na mũndũ wĩ </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ngoma thũku; nake akĩgũũthũka, akiuga: </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũhoro witũ nawe ũkĩrĩ ũrĩkũ, wee Yesu wa Nazareth?</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ũũkĩte gũtũnina? Nĩ ngũũĩ, nĩwe ũrĩa mũtheru wa Ngai.  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Yesu akĩmĩkaania, akiuga: Kira, na uume thĩinĩ wake. </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo ngoma ĩo thũku a mũthiora na ya kaya </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na mũgambo mũnene, ĩkiuma thĩinĩ  wake.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Andũ othe magĩkĩgega, magĩitĩka kũũrania atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ũguo nĩ atĩa-ĩ? Nĩ ũhoro mwerũ-nĩ ũyũ!</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngoma thũku o nacio aciathaga na hinya, na ikamũigua.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nayo ngumo yake  hingo ĩo ĩkĩhunja guothe, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ĩkĩiyũra bũrũri wothe wa Galilea mwena ũcio.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani
(NI TWAGUKUMIA WE KRISTO)</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA INYA MWAK B"},{Guid:"vRHg2zP7CEK2UByqiZ1GKQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Kumbukumbu la Torati 18: 15-20</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Kumbukumbu la Torati</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Musa aliwaambia wana wa Israeli, \"Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu wako atakusimamishia, kati ya nduguzo, </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nabii kama mimi, msikilizeni. </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndilo neno hilo 
ulilomwomba Bwana Mungu </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wako pale Horebu siku ile ya mkutano: </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>'Nisikilize tena sauti ya Bwana Mungu wangu </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala nisiangalie tena moto ule mkuu, nisife. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>' Naye Bwana akaniambia: Hayo waliyosema ni sawa. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitawasimamishia kati ya ndugu zao nabii afananaye nawe,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nitamtia kinywani mwake maneno yangu naye </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atawaambia kila nitakachowaamuru. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kama mtu hasikilizi maneno yangu atakayosema </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>huyu kwa jina langu, basi mimi mwenyewe nitamdai </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mtu huyu. Lakini ikiwa nabii anayethubutu kusema </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa jina langu neno 
nisilomwamuru mimi, </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akisema kwa jina la miungu mingine, nabii huyu atakufa.\"</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. (TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA	
Zaburi 95: I-2,6-7,7d-9</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K. Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Njoni, tumpigie BWANA kelele za furaha; </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tumshangilie mwamba wa wokovu wetu.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tuje mbele yake kwa 
shukrani, tumfanyie </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>shangwe kwa nyimbo na zaburi. </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K. Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Njoni, tuabudu na kusujudu; Tumpigie magoti </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>BWANA aliyetuumba
Kwani yeye ni Mungu wetu,</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>sisi lakini ni watu wa nıalisho yake, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kondöö wanaochungwa kwa mkono wake.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K. Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ingekuwa heri leo 
msikie saıuti yake! </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu kama huko Meriba, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kama baba zenu walivyokuwa siku ya Masa jangwani.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waliponijaribu, baba zenu waliponipima; </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ijapo walikwishaona 
matendo yangu. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K. Ingekuwa heri leo msikie sauti yake!</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Msiifanye mioyo yenu kuwa migumu.</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI
I Wakorintho 7:32.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Wakorintho</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndugu zangu: Nataka msiwe na shughuli. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Asiye na mke anashughulikia 
mambo ya Bwana, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ampendeze Mungu. Bali aliye na mke hushughulikia </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mambo ya ulimwengu, 
ampendeze mkewe. </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huelekea huko na huko. 
Kadhalika mwanamke </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>asiyeolewa au bikira 
huwaza mambo ya Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>apate kuwa mtakatifu mwili na roho.
Lakini aliyeolewa </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hushughulikia mambo 
ya ulimwengu huu, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ampendeze mumewe. Nasema hayo kwa kuwafaidia, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>si kwa kuwategea tanzi bali kwa kuwapa </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>heshima ya kumtumikia
Bwana daima pasipo </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuvutwa na mambo mengine.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI Mathayo 4:16</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.Aleluya. Watu wakaao gizani wameona mwanga mkuu. </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wenye kukaa katika nchi na uvuli wa mauti wameangazwa na nuru. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Marko</s></f>"},{ID:37,Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu aliingia katika sinagogi, akafundisha 
siku ya Sabato. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Watu walistaajabia mafundisho yake, kwa maana </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aliwafundisha kama mtu mwenye mamlaka </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na si kama Waandishi. Ndani ya sinagogi yao alikuwapo mtu </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amepagawa na pepo mchafu, akapaza sauti akisema,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Tuna nini nawe, Yesu wa Nazareti? Je, umekuja kutuangamiza?</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nakujua u nani, ndiwe Mtakatifu wa Mungu!\"</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yesu akamkemea akisema, \"Nyamaza! Umtoke!\" Pepo mchafu </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamtikisatikisa, 
akamtoka huku akilia kwa sauti kubwa.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Wote wakashangaa na wakaulizana, \"Kitu gani hiki? </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Haya ndiyo mafundisho mapya kwa mamlaka. Anawaamuru </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hata pepo wachafu, nao wanamtii.\" Na sifa yake mara </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ikaenea kila mahali 
katika ujirani wote wa Galilaya.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black>Injili ya Bwana. 
(SIFA KWAKO EE KRISTU)</f>"}],Style:{Background:{Brush:{Color:"FF000099"}}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA NNE YA MWAKA B"},{Guid:"tPvfVET/wEO4Jftvxu0NAw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA PILI YA KWARESIMA MWAKA B</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA
Mwanzo 22:1-2, 9a, 10-13,15</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Siku zile: Mungu alimjaribu 
Abrahamu, akamwambia: </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Abrahamu!\" Naye akaitika, 
\"Mimi hapa!\" Mungu akasema: </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umtwae mwanao Isaka, mwanao wa pekee umpendaye, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uende katika nchi ya Moria, na huko utamtoa sadaka </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ya kuteketezwa juu ya mlima nitakaokuonyesha.\"</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Walipofika mahali pale alipoambiwa na Mungu, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abrahamu akajenga hapo altare, akapanga kuni. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abrahamu akanyosha mkono, 
akashika kisu amchinje mwanawe.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini malaika wa Bwana akamwita toka mbinguni, akasema. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>“Abrahamu! Abrahamu!\" Naye akaitika, \"Mimi hapa!\" </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Malaika akasema,
\"Usimnyoshee mtoto mkono wako! </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Usimtende neno lolote! Sasa najua ya kuwa unamheshimu Mungu: </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hukunikatalia mwanao, mwanao wa pekee.\" </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abrahamu akainua macho, akaona kondoo dume</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amenaswa kichakani 
kwa pembe zake </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Abrahamu akaenda 
akamtwaa kondoo</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akamtoa sadaka ya kuteketezwa badala ya mwanawe. </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Malaika wa Bwana akamwita Abrahamu mara ya pili toka mbinguni, </s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akasema. \"Naapa kwa nafsi yangu, 
asema Bwana: </s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kwa kuwa umefanya jambo hilo wala hukunikatalia </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwanao, mwanao wa pekee, mimi nitakujaza baraka,</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nitaufanya uzao wako kuwa mwingi
kama nyota za mbinguni </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kama mchanga ulioko pwani ya bahari, tena utashinda mlango </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa maadui wake.
Katika uzao wako mataifa yote 
ya dunia </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yatajipatia baraka, 
kwa sababu umetii sauti yangu.\"</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana. 
(TUMSHUKURU MUNGU)</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> ZABURI YA KUTIKIZANA </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Zaburi 
116:10 na 15, 16 17, 12 19(K.9)</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kiitikio; Nitatembea mbele zake Bwana katika nchi za walio hai</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niliamini hata niliposema. \"Mimi nimetaabika sana\"</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kina thamani kubwa machoni pa Bwana kifo cha watakatifu wake. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>K. Nitatembea mbele zake Bwana katika nchi za walio hai</s></f>"},{ID:36,
