Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GÜTHOMA INJIRI YA M</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>Ứ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>THURE MARIKO:</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hindī īo Yesu agitwara Petro na Jakubu akīmakinyia kīrīma kīraya igūrù </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o oiki hatarī mūndū ũngī: akīgarūrūka ūrĩa aahanaga o hau maarī. </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nguo ciake igīkenga, igītuika njerū cũa: gūtirī mūthambia wa nguo gũükū </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thĩ ùngīhota gūcierūhia ûguo. Na makiumīrirūo nī Elia me na Musa nao makirianiria na Yesu. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake Petro agīcokia ūhoro, 
akīīra Yesu atīri: Mwonania, </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nì twagīrīirūo güikara gūkū: na nĩ twake ithūnù ithatū, kĩmwe gīaku, </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kimwe kĩa Musa, na kimwe kia Elia. Amu nĩ aarigītwo nĩ ũrīa angicokia; </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondū ni maagwatītwo nī guoya mũnene. Ningī gūgīūka itu rīkīmahumbĩra: </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na thĩinī wa itu gūkiuma 
mūgambo ūkiuga atīrī: </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Üyũ nĩwe Mūrù wakwa 
nyendete mūno: mûiguagei. </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na kahinda o kanini, maacoka kùroranga, makīaga gūcoka kuona mũndū, tiga o Yesu wiki e hamwe </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao, na rìrīa maaikūrūkaga kīrīma, akīmakaania matikere mũndù maùndù macio monete </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tiga o rīrĩa Mùrũ wa mùndù agakorūo arīkitie kũriūka oimite kwi aria akuù. </s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nao magitùùra mamenyereire
kiugo kīu, na makoranagia o ene nĩ atīa ūguo, kùriùka kuuma kùrî aria akuù.</s></f>"},{ID:71,
