Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GlTHOMO KlA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA INJIRI YA MÜTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hindi io, Arutwo makiheana ùhoro wa maûndù maria moneire njira-ini, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ùria emenyithirie küri o na ündů wa kwenyüra mugate, </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ningi o makiaragia maùndù macio ri, 
We mwene akirügama </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gatagati-ini kao, akimera atiri: Mürogia na thayů. Nao magituika nda </s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>magigiitigira mùno, makīīgereria ati nī ngoma mekuona. Nake akimera atiri: </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mùgùtangika niki? Na ni ki gigūtūma mùgie na mathangania </s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngoro-ini cianyu? Rorai moko makwa, o na maguru makwa, ati ni nii </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mwene, 'hambaatani, mwionere; 
ni gùkorüo ngoma </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndiri mwiri na mahindi ta ûù mukuona ndi nacio, </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na aarikia kuuga uguo, akimonia moko make, o na magūrù. Nao </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maakorūo matarī maretīkia nĩ ũndũ wa ûrīa makenete na makagega-rî, </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>akìmoria atiri: Mùri na irio haha? Nao makimūhe gīcunji gīa kĩũngūyù </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kīhīhie. Nake agīkīoya, akiriamakīīonagīra. Agīcoka akīmera atīrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lci nīcio ciugo ciakwa iria ndamwirire 
rìrīa ndatùire na inyuī, </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ngĩmwĩra atī: Gūtirī hingo maūndū mothe matakahingio, </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o marīa maandikitwo ūhoro wakwa watho-inī wa Musa, o na </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mabuku-inì ma Anabii, o na thaburi-inì. Hìndi o agīcoka akīmahe </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ūūgī, mamenye wega Maandīko: 
agikimera atīrī, Uũ nīguo ūhoro </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wandīkītwo Maandīko-inī atīrī, atī no mùhaka Kristù </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>anyaririke, na acoke kùriūka oime kūrī arīa akuŭ mūthenya wa </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gatatù; no ningī at</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ùhoro wa kwìrira na kuohanirùo mehia ūkahunjĩrio </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndūrīrī ciothe na rĩĩtwa rīake, na kwambìririo o kùu Jerusalem. </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na inyui ni inyuĩ aira a maũndũ macio.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846> Injiri Theru ya Mwathani.
(NITWAGUKUMIA WEE KRISTU)</s></f>"}],
