Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>agikararanagia nao; magagīcaria ūrīa mangīhota kümùùraga. </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nao ariù a lthe witù mamenya ühoro ücio, makīmüthereria </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Cesarea, makimūtūma Tarso. Naguo Kanitha ürīa warī Judea </s></f>"},{ID:16,
