Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RĨA MŨRATHI ISAIA: </s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwaka  o ũrĩa mũthamaki Ozia aakuire, nĩguo ndonire Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aikarĩire gĩtĩ gĩa ũthamaki kĩigĩtwo igũrũ kũndũ gũtũũgĩru;</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nacio nguo ciake ikaiyũra hekarũ nĩ ũndũ wa ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciaraihĩte.  Na igũrũ rĩake hakarũgama Aserafi, o Serafi ũmwe </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akagĩa na mathagu matandatũ. Nao o ũmwe akaanĩrĩra akera ũrĩa </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ũngĩ atĩrĩ: Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita, nĩwe mũtheru, ĩĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ti itheru, nĩwe mũtheru; thĩ yothe ĩiyũrĩtwo nĩ riri wake.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nacio itina cia hingĩro cia mĩromo ikĩenyenya nĩ ũndũ wa mũgambo </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wa ũcio waanagĩrĩra,
nayo nyũmba ikĩiyũra ndogo.  </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niĩ na niĩ ngĩkiuga atĩrĩ: Hĩ! Kaĩ ndĩ na haaro-ĩ! Nĩ ũndũ ndirĩ ho rĩu;</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gũkorũo ndĩ mũndũ wĩ mĩromo ĩtarĩ mĩtheru, o na ningĩ ndũũraga </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>thĩinĩ wa andũ matarĩ mĩromo mĩtheru; amu 
maitho makwa</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ monete Mũthamaki, o we Mwathani Mũnene wa Ita.  </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo Serafi ũmwe akĩũmbũka agĩũka harĩ niĩ, anyitĩte ikara rĩa </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwaki na guoko, arĩrutĩte kĩgongona-inĩ na mĩĩhato; agĩkĩhutia </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kanua  narĩo, akiuga ũũ: 
Atĩrĩrĩ, rĩrĩ nĩ rĩakũhutia mĩromo, </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo ũũru waku nĩ weherio, o namo mehia maku maahoroherio.  </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngĩcoka ngĩigua mũgambo wa Mwathani, akiuga atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nũ ũngĩrekia, ningĩ-rĩ, nũ ũgũtũthiĩra? Hĩndĩ ĩo ngĩkiuga 
atĩrĩ: </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Niĩ ũyũ haha; ta ndekia arĩ niĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GŨCOKERŨO                                         Thaburi 138:1-2a;2b-3;4-5;7b-8</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:                                               
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ngũgũcokeria ngatho na ngoro yakwa yothe, ngũkũinĩra </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngĩkũgoocaga ngai ciothe irĩ o ho.
Ngũinamĩrĩra  njerekeire  hekarũ yaku theru.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Njokerie rĩĩtwa rĩaku ngatho nĩ ũndũ wa ũtugi waku, na tondũ wa </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩhokeku waku o naguo,
nĩ kũnenehia ũnenehetie </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uuge waku kũrĩ maũndũ marĩa mangĩ ma 
rĩĩtwa rĩaku mothe.  </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mũthĩ o ũrĩa ndetanire, wee nĩ wanyamũkĩire; 
nĩ wanyũmĩrĩirie nĩ kũnjĩkĩra hinya ngoro.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Athamaki othe a thĩ nĩ ngatho  magagũcokeria, wee Mwathani, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>rĩrĩa magakorũo maiguĩte ciugo iria kanua gaku kaanoiga. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ĩĩ-ni, nĩ kũina makaina, magane ikĩro cia Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>riri wa Mwathani nĩ mũnene.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Guoko gwaku kwa ũrĩo nĩkuo gũkahonokia, Mwathani-rĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maũndũ makwa nĩ akamakindĩra: ũtugi waku, Mwathani, nĩ wa </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tene na tene; wĩra wa moko maku-rĩ, ndũkanaũtiganĩrie.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA:	
Mbere ya araika nĩ ngũkũgoca wee Mwathani</s></f>"},{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA IGĨRĨ 
1 Akorintho 15:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA MARŨA MA MŨTHURE  PAUL KŨRĨ ANDŨ A KORINTHO MARĨA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ariũ a Ithe witũ, ngũcoka kũmũmenyithia Injiri </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndamũhunjĩirie, o ĩrĩa mwetĩkirie na noguo mũtũire mũrũmĩtie;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningĩ nĩguo ũtũmaga mũhonoke, mwakorũo mũgũtũũra </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mũnyitĩte ciugo iria ndamũhunjĩirie ũhoro ũcio nacio,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tiga mũkorirũo mwawĩtĩkirie tũhũ. O mbere-rĩ, ndaambĩrĩirie </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũmũhe  ũhoro  o ũrĩa  niĩ ndaamũkĩrire,
na nĩguo </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atĩ Kristũ nĩ aakuire nĩ ũndũ wa mehia maitũ, o ta ũrĩa Maandĩko moigĩte; </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na atĩ nĩ aathikirũo: na atĩ mũthenya wa gatatũ akĩriũkio ta ũrĩa Maandĩko </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>macio maakiugĩte; na atĩ akĩũmĩrĩra Cefa;</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agĩcoka akiũmĩrĩra andũ arĩa ikũmi  na erĩ. Thutha wa ũguo ningĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiumĩrĩra ariũ a Ithe witũ Magana matano na magakira,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmoimĩrĩra o ihinda rĩmwe othe, nao andũ acio-rĩ, arĩa aingĩ marĩ o ho </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na rĩu, no amwe nĩ gũkoma makomete.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thutha ũcio akiumĩrĩra Jakobu; na thutha wa ũguo akiumĩrĩra atũmwo </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>othe; na thutha wa acio angĩ othe, akĩnyũmĩrĩra o na niĩ, ndariĩ ta mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>waciarirũo atarĩ mũkinyu.  Nĩ 
gũkorũo nĩ niĩ ũrĩa mũnyinyi wa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>atũmwo arĩa angĩ, na ndiagĩrĩirũo nĩ gwĩtagwo mũtũmwo, nĩ ũndũ nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndanyaririre kanitha wa Ngai. No rĩrĩ, Wega wa Ngai nĩguo ũtũmĩte </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nduĩke ũũ ndariĩ; naguo Wega wake ũcio ndakinyĩirio ndwatuĩkire wa </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũhũ, no nĩ ndarutire wĩra ngĩĩnogagia mũno gũkĩra acio angĩ </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>othe; no ti niĩ ndarutaga wĩra ũcio, nĩ Wega wa Ngai ũcio warĩ </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hamwe na niĩ waũrutaga. Tondũ ũcio-rĩ, o na </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kũngĩtuĩka atĩ nĩ niĩ kana nĩ acio, ũhoro  ũcio noguo </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tũhunjagia, na noguo inyuĩ mwetĩkirie. </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ciugo cia Mwathani</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>RŨĨMBO RWA INJIRI
John 15,16
	</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alleluya. Alleluya. Mwathani ekuga atĩrĩ: Ti inyuĩ mwathurire  niĩ, </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ niĩ ndamũthurire inyuĩ, ngĩmwamũra, nĩ getha mũthiĩ mũciare maciaro, </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>namo maciaro manyu matũũre. Alleluia</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĨTHOMO KĨA INJIRI
Luka 5:1-11</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GŨTHOMA INJIRI YA MŨTHURE LUKA:</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hĩndĩ ĩo nĩ gwatwĩkire atĩ hĩndĩ ĩmwe rĩrĩa andũ aingĩ </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mamũhatĩkaga nĩ getha maigwe mũgambo wa Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>we nĩ arũgamĩte rũtere-inĩ rũa iria rĩa Jenezareth, Yesu nĩ onire </s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngarawa igĩrĩ ciikaire rũtere-inĩ rũa iria rĩu;</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>no atahi a ciũngũyũ nĩ moimĩte  thĩinĩ wacio, na nĩ gũthambia </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maathambagia ngara ciao cia ndigi. 
Nake agĩtonya </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngarawa ĩmwe yarĩ Simone, akĩmũthaitha amĩtwaratware  </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>hanini, yume  rũtere-inĩ. Agĩcoka agĩikara thĩ, akĩruta kĩrĩndĩ ũhoro, arĩ </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngarawa-inĩ. Na aatiga kwaria, akĩĩra Simone atĩrĩ:</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ta twaratwara ngarawa harĩa hariku, mũikũrũkie ngara cianyu cia </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndigi iria-inĩ mũtahe ciũngũyũ. Nake Simone akĩmũcokeria </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akĩmwĩra atĩrĩ: Mwonania, nĩ tũrutĩre wĩra wa hinya ũtukũ wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na tũtinagwatia kĩndũ o na kĩ: no rĩrĩ, nĩ ũndũ wa kiugo kĩu gĩaku </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ ngũikũrũkia ngarairia cia ndigi. Nao maarĩkia gwĩka ũguo, magĩtaha </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciũngũyũ nyingĩ ma; nacio ngara ciao cia ndigi igĩtuĩkatuĩka;</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nao makĩheneria arĩa maarutithanagia wĩra nao, </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>marĩ ngarawa-inĩ iria ingĩ, atĩ moke mamateithie. </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Magĩgĩũka makĩiyũria ngarawa icio cierĩ ki, nacio ikĩenda kũhorokera </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>maaĩ-inĩ. Nake Simone Petro ona ũguo, akĩinamĩrĩra maru-inĩ  ma Yesu, </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akiuga atĩrĩ:Ta njeherera, Mwathani, nĩ gũkorũo ndĩ mũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwĩhia. Nĩ ũndũ we, o na andũ othe arĩa maarĩ hamwe nake, nĩ maagĩĩtwo </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ kĩgeganio nĩ ũndũ wa ciũngũyũ icio nyingĩ maatahĩte;</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na gwata Jakobu na John, ariũ a Zebedeo, arĩa maarutithanagia </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wĩra na Simone. Nake Yesu akĩĩra Simone atĩrĩ: Tiga gwĩtigĩra, nĩ ũndũ </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kuuma rĩu nĩ ũrĩtahaga andũ. Nao maarĩkia gũtwara ngarawa </s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciao rũtere-inĩ, magĩtiga indo ciao ciothe, makĩmũrũmĩrĩra.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injiri theru ya Mwathani </s></f>"}],
