ni Muoyo Mūtheru. akimera atīrî: </s></f>"},{ID:5,Style:{Background:{Image:"Blue Sky over Field.jpg"}},
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Inyui anene a k</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rindi o na athuri, 
kũngīkorūo ũmūthi ni kūūrio ühoro </s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wa wiko ūcio mwega ūrekırúo mùndù ūcio ūratũire e kīonje, </s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na ūrīa arahonirio-rī, menyai inyuothe, o na andū </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>othe a Israel, atiri, ati ũndū ùraūtūmĩte mũndū ūcio </s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>arūgame haha mbere yanyu, arĩ mũgima, nĩ rĩri, nì rīĩtwa rīa </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yesu Kristū wa Nazareti, ūrīa inyuĩ mwambithirie mūtĩ igūrũ, nake </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ngai akīmūriūkia oime kũrī arīa akuũ. Nĩwe Ihiga rīrĩa rīaregirūo nĩ </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>inyui aaki, na nĩrĩo rītuikite riria inene rīa </s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>koine. Naguo ūhoro wa kūhonokio ndūngīoneka harì ūngi </s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o na ūrikū: nìündū atirī, gūtirī rīitwa rĩngī rĩanaheanwo gūkū </s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>thĩ küri andi rĩngīagīrira rīa gùtūhonokia.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani. 
(MWATHANI AGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>THABURI YA GŪCOKERŪO 
Thaburi l18: 1. 8 9: 21</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ihiga rīrīa riaregirũo nĩ aaki, nĩrīo rītuikīte o riria inene rīa koine.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>I gīcokeriei Mwathani ngaatho, 
tondũ nĩ mwega; </s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ ūtugi wake nī wa tene na tene. Nĩ wega kūrahĩra Mwathani </s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>gūkīra kwihoka andū. Ni wega kùrahira Mwathani gūkīra kwihoka anene</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ihiga rīrīa riaregirũo nĩ aaki, nĩrīo rītuikīte o riria inene rīa koine.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nĩ ngatho ngūgùcokeria, tondū ni ûnyamūkiirie, ůgagituika </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ûhonokio wakwa. Ihiga riria riaregirûo ni aaki nĩrio rituikīte </s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o rìria inene ria koine. Undù ùcio uumite </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwi Mwathani, na nì ügūtùgegia tùkiwona.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ihiga rīrīa riaregirũo nĩ aaki, nĩrīo rītuikīte o riria inene rīa koine.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mürathimwo-rī nī ûrīa wa gùùka 
na rĩitwa ria Mwathani! </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Twi gūku nyümba ya Mwathani, 
inyui nī twamùrathima, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wee ùria Mùrungu wakwa, no ngùcokerie ngatho: wee ùri Ngai </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wakwa, ni ngūgūtùùgiria. I gicokeriei Mwathani ngatho, </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondu ni mwega; tondù ûtugi wake nì wa tene na tene.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ICOKIA: Ihiga rīrīa riaregirũo nĩ aaki, nĩrīo rītuikīte o riria inene rīa koine.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
