1 Johana 3: 1-2 </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GÜTHOMA MARŪA MA MŪTHURE JOHANA MARİA MA MBERE:</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ariù a lthe witū, onei wendani 
uria ūkinenehete, üria Ithe witù </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atwendete naguo, atī tùtuwo ciana cia Ngai; na niguo tùtuikite. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Tondù ùcio andù a gūkù thì matitùùi, nì ũndù o nake </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>matiamůmenyire. Edwa akwa, riu tũrĩ ciana cia Ngai, na gùtiri </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kùramenyithanio ùrīa tùgaikara thutha. Ni t</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>uu</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>i ati </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>o riria we akonithanio, tùkahaanana </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nake; nì gūkorùo tūkamuona o ùria atarii.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ciugo cia Mwathani.
(MWATHANI AROGATHWO)</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>RWlMBO RWA ALLELUYA 
Johana 10:14</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alleluya, Alleluya. Mwathani ekuuga: Ni nĩ nii mùrithi ūrīa mwega; ni njùi </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ng'ondu ciakwa mwene, o nacio ng'ondu ciakwa nī injūi. Alleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
