Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Andū arīa aaramu a thĩ othe nĩ kũrĩa m</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>a</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>karīa na mamuinamirie </s></f>"},{ID:29,
