Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nakuo küümīriria kūu gütũmaga tügīe na gwīkindĩra, </s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>naguo wikindīru ücio ügatūma tūgīe na wirigíriro,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wirigiriro ücio ndüngīgatüma műndū akehokokwo, </s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gükorūo wendani wa Ngai nĩ üitīrīirűo ngoro-inĩ </s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ciitű nĩ ündű wa güikarūo nī Muoyo Mūtheru ürīa twaheirűo.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GiTHOMO KIA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>John 
16: 12- 15.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MUTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hĩndī io Yesu nĩ erire arūmīrīri ake : Nĩ ndigairie </s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maűndũ maingi ma kūmwira, 
no mütingihota kūmetiiria rīu. </s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>No rĩrĩ, ücio Muoyo wa ma oka, we nī akamūtongoria </s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>amuumīririe ühoro ini
ürīa wa ma wothe; </s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tondũ ndakaaragia na kwira gwake mwene, indī </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>maŭnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ủ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> o mothe marīa akaigua, nomo akoiga; </s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na nĩ akamuumbürira maűndű marīa magoka thutha, Ne nĩ niĩ akagoocithia; </s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nĩ gūkorűo nĩ maündű makwa akanyitaga, amuumbüragīre, </s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maūndũ o mothe marīa lthe witű e namo nī makwa; </s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nīkĩo ndoiga atī nĩ maűndū makwa akanyitaga, amuumbūragire inyuí.</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"}],
Text:"KIUMIA KIA UTATU MUTHERU MWAKA C"},{Guid:"lev87XbONEmhMArrVs+yLQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<u><fArial Black><s1384>SHEREHE YA UTATU MTAKATIFU MWAKA C</s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA KWANZA
Mithali 8:22-3 1</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika kitabu cha Mithali</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hekima ya Mungu asema hivi:
Bwana ameniumba tangu mwanzo wa njia zake,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>malimbuko ya kazi zake alizofanya tangu asili:
tangu wakati wa kale nimeumbwa,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tangu mwanzo, kabla ya dunia kuwapo.
kabla vilindi havijakuwapo, nalizaliwa,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kabla ya chemchemi zenye kujaa maji;
kabla milima haijawekwa imara,</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kabla ya vilima, nilikuwa nimezaliwa;
kabla Mungu hajaumba nchi wala mashamba,</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala udongo wa kwanza wa dunia.
Alipoziweka mbingu, nilikuwapo,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>alipopiga mstari kuzungukia bahari kuu;
alipoweka imara mawingu mahali pa juu,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kukaza chemchemi za bahari mahali pake,
alipoiwekea bahari mipaka yake,</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>yaani maji yasipite ukingo wake;
aliposimika misingi ya dunia,</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hapo nilikuwa kama fundi wa kazi pamoja naye;
siku kwa siku nikawa furaha yake,</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nikicheza mbele yake wakati wote.
Nikicheza juu ya uso wa dunia yake,</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na furaha yangu kuwa pamoja na wanadamu.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana </s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Zaburi 84-5, 6-7, 8-9 (K. 2a)</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, jinsi lilivyo tukufu jina lako duniani kote!</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Nikiziangalia mbingu zako, kazi ya vidole vyako,
mwezi na nyota ulizozipangilia</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mtu ni kitu gani hata umkumbuke
na mwanadamu ni nini hata umjali? K.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, jinsi lilivyo tukufu jina lako duniani kote!</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umemfanya mdogo kidogo chini ya mungu,
umemvika taji la utukufu na heshima.</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Umempa mamlaka juu ya kazi za mikono yako.
Umeviweka vitu vyote chini ya miguu yake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, jinsi lilivyo tukufu jina lako duniani kote!</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kondoo na ng'ombe wote.
hata wanyama wa porini,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndege wa angani, na samaki wa baharini.
kila kiumbe kitembeacho njia za baharini. K.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Ee Bwana, jinsi lilivyo tukufu jina lako duniani kote!</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SOMO LA PILI</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Warumi </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>5:1-5</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Warumi</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndugu zangu: Kwa kuwa tumekubaliwa uadilifu kwa nguvu ya imani, </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>tuna amani na Mungu kwa njia ya Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo. </s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika imani, huyo ametuwezesha kuingia hali ya neema tuliyo nayo sasa</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa sababu ya neema hiyo twafurahia matumaini ya kushiriki
utukufu wa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini hatufurahii hayo tu, bali twafurahia
vile vile mateso.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Maana twajua kwamba mateso huleta subira; </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>subira huleta uthabiti. na uthabiti huleta matumaini.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini matumaini hayadanganyi, kwa maana upendo wa Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>umeenezwa mioyoni mwetu na Roho Mtakatifu tuliyempokea,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
Ufunuo 1:8</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Aleluya. W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Atukuzwe Baba na Mwana na Roho Mtakatifu</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mungu aliyeko,
aliyekuwako na anayekuja.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>W. Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yohane 16:12- 15</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo la Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wakati ule:
Yesu aliwaambia wafuasi wake:</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>\"Ninayo bado mengi ya kuwaambia,
lakini sasa hamwezi kuyavumilia bado.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini atakapokuja yeye, Roho wa ukweli,
atawaongoza katika ukweli wote.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana hatasema yake mwenyewe,
ila atakayoyasikia atayasema</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na kuwatangazia ninyi mambo yajayo.
Yeye atanitukuza,</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa maana atatwaa katika yale yaliyo yangu
na kuwatangazia ninyi.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yote Baba aliyo nayo ni yangu;
kwa hiyo nalisema ya kwamba</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>atatwaa katika yale yaliyo yangu
na kuwatangazia ninyi.\"</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],
