Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>DOMINIKA YA PILI
BAADA YA KUZALIWA KWAKE BWANA</s></f>",IsDisplayed:0},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA KWANZA</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Hekima ya Bwana imekaa kwa watu wateule.\"</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika kitabu cha Yoshua bin Sira</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hekima atajisifu nafsi yake,</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na katikati ya watu wake atajitukuza.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atafungua kinywa chake katika mkutano wa Aliye Juu,</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na atajitukuza mbele ya uweza wake.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hapo Muumba vitu vyote aliniamuru,
na aliyeniumba</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mimi aliipumzisha hema yangu,
akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>'Weka maskani yako kwa Yakobo,
na urithi wako katika Israeli.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yoshua bin
Kabla ya milele yote, tangu mwanzo</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aliniumba,
nami sitakoma hata milele.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika hema takatifu, mbele yake nilihudumia, </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na hivyo nilithibitishwa katika Sioni.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika mji wa kupendeza alinipumzisha,</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na utawala wangu u katika Yerusalemu.
Nikatia mizizi katika watu watukufu,</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>katika sehemu ya BWANA na urithi wake.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Zaburi 147:12-13, 14</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno alifanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Umtukuze Bwana, ee Yerusalemu:
umsifu Mngu wako, ee Sion</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwani amekaza komeo za malango yako,</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amewabariki wana wako ndani yako.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> 
Neno alifanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ameweka amani mipakani mwako,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>anakushibisha kwa unono wa ngano.</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hupeleka amri yake duniani,
neno lake lapiga mbio sana!</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> 
Humjulisha Yakobo neno lake,
Israeli amri na kanuni zake.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hakulitendea taifa jingine lolote lile hayo;
wala hawakuzijua kanuni zake.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SOMO LA PILI</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Waefeso 1:3-6, 15-18</s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Somo katika barua ya Mtakatifu Paulo kwa Waefeso</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atukuzwe Mungu, Baba wa Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo:</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>yeye
ametubariki katika Kristo kwa baraka</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>zote za mbinguni zitokazo
kwa Roho Mtakatifu. </s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika yeye ametuchagua kabla ya kuwekwa
misingi ya ulimwengu, kusudi tuwe</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> watakatifu na bila doa mbele
yake katika upendo.</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Toka mwanzo aliazimia kutufanya watoto wake kwa njia ya Yesu
Kristo, </s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kama alivyotaka kwa mapenzi yake,</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kusudi tuisifu na kuitikiza  neema yake aliyotujalia katika huyo mpendwa.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nimesikia imani kwa Bwana Yesu kati yenu na upendo kwa
watakatifu wote.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa hiyo siachi kumshukuru Mungu kwa ajili
yenu,</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> na kuwakumbuka daima katika sala zangu, ili Mungu wa
Bwana wetu Yesu Kristo,</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Baba wa utukufu, awapeni roho ya
hekima na ya ufunuo mpate kumjua yeye. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Macho ya mioyo yenu
yaangazwe, mpate kung'amua:</s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kuitwa naye kwaleta tumaini lipi,
na jinsi</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utukufu atakaowarithisha watakatifu wake unavyozidi.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>SHANGILIO LA INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.
Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Utukufu kwako, ee Kristo, ulihubiriwa kati ya mataifa;</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utukufu kwako, ee Kristo, uliaminiwa ulimwenguni </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aleluya.</s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>INJILI</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yohane I:1-18</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwanzo wa Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mwanzoni kulikuwako Neno, naye Neno alikuwa kwa Mungu.
Na Neno huyu alikuwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huyu mwanzoni alikuwako kwa Mungu.
Kwa Neno vyote vimeumbwa,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na pasipo Neno hakikuumbwa chochote kilichoumbwa.</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndani yake ulikuwamo uzima,
na uzima ulikuwa ni mwanga wa wanadamu;</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mwanga huo uliangaza gizani, lakini giza halikuupokea.</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Palitokea mtu ametumwa na Mungu, jina lake Yohane.</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huyo alikuja kutoa ushuhuda, apate kuushuhudia mwanga
ili wote wasadiki kwa sababu yake.</s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Yeye hakuwa ule mwanga,
ila wajibu wake ulikuwa kuushuhudia ule mwanga.</s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alikuwako mwanga halisi amwangaziaye kila mtu,
alikuwa ulimwenguni humu.</s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alikuwako ulimwenguni, nao ulimwengu uliumbwa kwa njia yake,
lakini ulimwengu haukumtambua.</s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Alifika kwa walio wake, nao walio wake hawakumpokea.</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Lakini wote waliompokea aliwapa uwezo wa kuwa watoto wa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ndio wale wasadikio kwa jina lake,
waliozaliwa, si kwa damu,</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>wala kwa tamaa ya mwili,
Wala kwa tamaa ya mwanadamu bali kwa mapenzi ya Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Neno akafanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu; nasi tumeuona utukufu wake,</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>utukufu kama wa mzaliwa wa pekee wa Baba,</s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>amejaa neema na kweli Yohane alimshuhudia na alipaza sauti akasema,</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Huyu ndiye niliyemtaja niliposema,</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Anayekuja nyuma yangu amekuwa mbele yangu,
kwa maana alikuwa kabla yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Katika ukamilifu wake sisi sote tumepokea neema juu ya neema.</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwa maana sheria imetolewa kwa njia ya Musa,</s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>lakini neema na kweli zimepatikana kwa Yesu Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Hakuna aliyemwona Mungu.
Mwana wa pekee,</s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mungu,
aliye kifuani mwa Baba, amemtambulisha kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],Style:{Background:{BodyRect:"0,0,10000,9300"}},
Text:"DOMINIKA YA PILI 
BAADA YA KUZALIWA KWAKE BWANA
"},{Guid:"w25H0BmnGUWkXZjMeNb/MQ",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GUTHOMA KUUMA IBUKU RIA SIRACH :</s></f>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ugī nīguo wīgathagīrīria, ūrīa gatagatīinī ka andūũ aguo nĩ wīkumagia.</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ ühingūraga kanua kaguo nyūmba-inī ya Urīa ürī Igūrū ma.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ wikumagia thĩinī waguo rīrīa ürĩ hakuhī na Mwene Hinya :</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>\"Ni ndoimire kanua-inī ka Urĩa ürī Igūrű ma, na ndahumbire thĩ ta mūndū.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Kūrīa njikarīte nī igūrūma, na gītī gīakwa kīrī igūrű rĩa matu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake mūmbi wa indo ciothe nī anjathire, </s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ūrīa wanyũmbire nī aheire handū ha kwamba hama.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nake akīnjīra atīrī: Aka hama yaku thīinī wa
Yakobu, tua Israel igai rīaku. </s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tene, tene, kīambīrīria-inī, nĩrīo anyūmbire, na ngatūüra mīndĩ na
mĩndī. </s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ndamūtungatagīra ndī mbere yake thĩinī wa nyűmba irīa theru, </s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kwa ūguo ngatūūra thĩinī wa Sion, Na thīinī wa Jerusalem nĩ njigīte wathani wakwa.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> Nĩ handīte mīrita thĩinī wa andū agītīo, o na thīinī wa indo cia Mwathani, nĩ cio igai rīake.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>THABURI YA GÜCOKERŪO</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thaburi 147: 12-13;14-1 5;1 9-20.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Uuge wa Ngai nĩ agīgītunka mūndūũ na agītū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>rania na ithuĩ. </s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Gooca Mwathani, wee Jerusalem;</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> kirahe Ngai waku, wee Sion!</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Amu mīgīko ya ihingo ciaku
nĩ amikīrīte hinya;</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>kūu gwaku thiini-ri, nĩ arathimīte ciana ciaku.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Uuge wa Ngai nĩ agīgītuika mūndū na agītū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>rania na ithuĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Atūmīte gwaku gutūure thayūo nginya ndere, </s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na ni akūhūnagia ngano, o îrīa īri ūnoru.</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Arekagia uuge wake ūgakinya gūkū thi;</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ūhoro wake nī ūhanyūkaga narua mũno,</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Uuge wa Ngai nĩ agīgītuika mūndū na agītū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>rania na ithuĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ühoro wake nī Yakobu oimagirīria, </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ni Israeli amenyithagia mītugo îrīa aathanīte,</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na matua
maria atuite, Ndarĩ eka rūrirī rūngī ta uguo;</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>matua macio make-ri, ndūriri itiri ciamamenya</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ICOKIA : Uuge wa Ngai nĩ agīgītuika mūndū na agītū</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>rania na ithuĩ.</s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GĪTHOMO KiÀ IGiRi</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Aefeso
1: 3-6: 15 - 18</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GUTHOMA MARŪA MA MUTHURE PAUL KŪRI ANDU A EFESO :</s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ngai arogoocwo, o we Ngai wa Mwathani witü Yesu Kristũ, na nowe Ithe, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>üria ütürathimte thiinií wa Kristű na irathimo</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ciothe cia muoyo, iria ciumaga Igūrũ, </s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>küringana na üria aatüthurire thiin</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>i</s></f><fArial Black><s2769> wake thĩ  itanombwo, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha tűtuīke atheru na twage kaüügű agītuona. </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Na tondű wa gütwenda-ri, nī aatuorereire o mbere nīguo </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tūtuīke ciana ciake nĩ ündũ wa Yesu Kristű, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>agīgiīka üguo nĩ ündű wa ürīa endete gütugana, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na nĩ getha Wega wake ürĩa üiyűire riri ükumagio, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o Wega ücio aatüitürürire
na ūtana thĩinī wake we üria endete műno.</s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ni ũndũ wa üguo, o na nii- rī, </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>tondű nĩ njiguite ühoro wa witikio ürīa mwītīkītie Mwathani Yesu naguo,</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na wendani ürīa mwendaga andü arīa othe aamüre naguo, </s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nditigithagīria gūcokia ngatho nĩ ündũ wanyu,</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngīműgwetaga mahoya-inī makwa;</s></f>"},{ID:51,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ngahoyaga atī Ngai wa Mwathani witü Yesu Kristü,</s></f>"},{ID:52,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o we Ithe witű mwene riri,</s></f>"},{ID:53,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aműhe omũndű muoyo wa kūműühīgia na wa kümüguüriria maündü,</s></f>"},{ID:54,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>muongererūo ūmenyi wa kūmenyana nake; </s></f>"},{ID:55,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>ningī ati maitho manyu ma ngoro mathererão nĩ ütheri, </s></f>"},{ID:56,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nī getha mümenye wega kīirigīrīro kīria mwitiirüo nīwe mügīe nakīo ; </s></f>"},{ID:57,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o na mūmenye üria igai riake riina riri rīingīhīte ta arĩ ūtonga műnene, </s></f>"},{ID:58,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>narīo nīrīo rĩa andü ake aamüre,</s></f>"},{ID:59,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icio nicio ciugo cia Mwathani,</s></f>"},{ID:60,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GITHOMO KIA INJIRI</s></f>"},{ID:61,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>John
 1: 1 -18.</s></f>"},{ID:62,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>GUTHOMA INJIRI YA MŪTHURE JOHN :</s></f>"},{ID:63,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>O kīambirīria-rī, Uge warī o kuo, naguo Uge watūire o harī Ngai, </s></f>"},{ID:64,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>o naguo Uge warī o Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:65,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ucio Uge - rī, nĩ aagīitūire harī Ngai o kīambĩrīria.</s></f>"},{ID:66,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Indo ciothe ikīgīa ciagīire na ündű wake,</s></f>"},{ID:67,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>na kindü
o gīothe kīrīa kīgīīte,</s></f>"},{ID:68,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gūtirī kīagiire we atarī ho, o na kīmwe. </s></f>"},{ID:69,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Thĩinī wake nīkuo kwarī muoyo,</s></f>"},{ID:70,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>naguo muoyo ūcio nīguo warī ūtheri wa andū. </s></f>"},{ID:71,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Naguo ūtheri nĩ ütūire o ütherete nduma-inī ,</s></f>"},{ID:72,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nayo
nduma ndīaūhootire. </s></f>"},{ID:73,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Nĩ gwokire mündū wareketio nī Ngai, wetagwo John.</s></f>"},{ID:74,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Mündü ücio okire
nĩ ündi wa ūira,</s></f>"},{ID:75,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>oimbūre ūhoro wa ūtheri ūcio, </s></f>"},{ID:76,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ getha andū othe metikie nĩ ündū wake.
Na tiwe ūtheri ūcio;</s></f>"},{ID:77,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>okire nī getha oimbūre ūhoro waguo, ütheri ücio. </s></f>"},{ID:78,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Ütheri küna, ürīa üműrikagira mũnd</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ữ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769> o wothe,</s></f>"},{ID:79,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nĩ warī kuo ūgiūkaga thĩ. We, Ütheri ūcio, </s></f>"},{ID:80,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>aarī gükūũ th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s2769>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s2769>, o nayo thĩ īkigia yagīire na ūndū wake,</s></f>"},{ID:81,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> nakīo kīrīndī gīa gūkű thĩ gīkīaga kümümenya. Okire gwake mwene ,</s></f>"},{ID:82,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>não andū ake o ene matiigana kūmwītikīra.</s></f>"},{ID:83,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> No arĩa othe maamwītikīrire, nĩo arīa mehokete riitwa rīake,</s></f>"},{ID:84,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> acio akīmahotithia gūtuīka ciana cia Ngai,</s></f>"},{ID:85,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>itaaciarirűo nĩ thakame, kana igīciarūo nĩ</s></f>"},{ID:86,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Kwenda kwa mwirī kana kwenda kwa mūndū, no Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:87,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>We, Uge -rī, agīgītuīka mūndū, agītūürania na ithuï aiyüirüo nĩ ütugi na</s></f>"},{ID:88,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769> 
ühoro-ūria-wa-ma, na ithuī tūkīīonera riri wake, </s></f>"},{ID:89,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>riri o ta wamwana wa mūmwe oimīte kürī Ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:90,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>John nĩ oimbūrīte ühoro wake, </s></f>"},{ID:91,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>akaanīrīra akoiga atīirī: Ocio nowe ndoigire, atī, </s></f>"},{ID:92,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>uria ügüüka thutha
wakwa nĩ agite mbere yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:93,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>nĩ gükorűo aari kuo mbere yakwa, Amu-rī, thiini wa küiyūruo küu</s></f>"},{ID:94,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>gwake twanaheo ithuothe, tügītugagwo ringī na rĩngī.</s></f>"},{ID:95,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Tondű watho watūmirüo na Musa; ütugi na uhoro-üria-wa-ma</s></f>"},{ID:96,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>mokire na Yesu Kristū, Gütirĩ mündü üri ona Ngai ;</s></f>"},{ID:97,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Müriü wa mümwe, üria gīthüri - inī gīa Ithe, nīwe uumbūrīte ühoro wake.</s></f>"},{ID:98,
Text:"<fArial Black><s2769>Icio nīcio ciugo cia Mwathani.</s></f>"}],
